strings: <voice_0x01001CA4><se_high>Media princess: You know, if I start drinking well water, I can talk to you in my dreams.
<voice_0x01001CA5><se_high>Media princess: I remember one day you said you were having a bad dream.
<voice_0x01001CA6><se_high>Media princess: You said you got lost in a cave with a giant dragon. I can't find a way out and you are being dragged under your feet!
<voice_0x01001CA7><se_high>Media princess: Call me if you have nightmares! I'll go find you there!
<voice_0x01001CA8><se_high>Media princess: At least we can have fun...
